node.text:
🍻GUAVA TOAST & RUBBER DUCKIES 🍻

One of the finest things in life is all that which you reserve for family; Those Sunday potlucks, chicken fights in the pool, talks of life and love, sipping lagers deep into the night 🌙

Uncle @dinosvino and everyone @vitaminseabrewing radiate what family is all about, always exuding all the love and respect they have to possibly give. We both wanted to toast to family, so we brewed up a lager as crispy as toast and conditioned it with a splash of guava. 

Sipping on Sundays is recommended. Don’t forget your rubber duckies🛁

🐤 🐤 🐤 🐤 🐤 🐤 🐤 🐤 🐤 🐤 🐤 
🐤GUAVA TOAST & RUBBER DUCKIES🐤
🐤 🐤 🐤 🐤 🐤 🐤 🐤 🐤 🐤 🐤 🐤

node.text:
💀BARRELS OF DEATH💀 

Here is to keeping things in their purest form. To Leaving them unadulterated and untouched by anything other than their essential and elemental characteristics. To insisting, with reckless abandon, certain things are just meant to be left alone; Unbothered, unchanged, unconditioned.

That’s exactly what we did with this stout: left it in its purest form. Aged 21 months in both Dominican Rum barrels and Woodford Reserve Bourbon barrels, we let the base and the barrels do the talking.

Silken Elegance in ever bottle.

☠️☠️☠️☠️☠️☠️☠️☠️☠️
☠️BARRELS OF DEATH☠️
☠️☠️☠️☠️☠️☠️☠️☠️☠️

Double Barrel Imperial Stout Aged 21 Months in Dominican Rum and Woodford Reserve Bourbon Barrels

🚀DUDE, WHERE’S MY ROCKET?👨🏽‍🚀

Ever start a company and use it’s profits to build yourself a rocket ? Yeah, neither have we 😅 but we can appreciate a hearty desire for experimentation and exploration, because hey.. we have to keep things eccentric and trippy 🍄 🍄 🍄

Sometimes you just have to shake things up, so in keeping with that sentiment we procured some EXPERIMENTAL hops and dosed a stellar DIPA so hazy it’ll have you singing with the birds up in space

Their Origin might not be Blue, but they’ll still have you floating with the stars 😉🤩

🦤🚀 🦤🚀 🦤🚀 🦤🚀 🦤🚀🦤

node.text:
⚓️LOAD OF BARNACLES⚓️

It’s that time of year again where we make our way down to the sea floor with our homies from @calusabrewing to find out who lives in a pineapple, maybe stop by trippyfish fields and pick some aquatic hops , and then make our way home just in time for supper and our first hop addition 😉

We transmute our experience into a liquid bountiful deep sea mosaic and galaxy, washed ashore by motueka, that elicits a full submersion of your taste buds. Although we traveled through crystalline waters to get these hops, HAZY is the only word to describe their gifts.

Take a sip, you might just get hit by a..

🦑🐠🐳🐚⚓️ 🦑🐠🐳🐚

👅 SKIP THE LINE 👅

There has been an energetic resurgence recently and over the last year it’s influenced a fresh culture of culinary pop-ups in Miami, and with it new emerging chefs worthy of attention. We’re sure you already have a few names swimming through your mind, and we know you’ve probably seen them in more than one place.. but have you seen them all under one roof ??? 🤔🤔 
Well here’s your chance..
Say Hello to our First Annual Doral Food and Beer Fest, curated together with our OG brother Julian Uribe from @gorillacitysandwiches :

🤤🔥SKIP THE LINE: DORAL FOOD AND BEER FESTIVAL🔥🤤

We will showcase some of Miami’s 🥵HOTTEST🥵 chefs, ranging from critically-acclaimed titans of industry to Food and Wine Fest award winners to the city’s hipest emerging chefs. They’ll have a smorgasbord of samples prepared for you, so you can just walk up and grab without having to wait in a line and place an order!! Here’s the best part… 🤯ALL YOU CAN EAT AND DRINK BABY!🤯 That’s right, you’ll be able to eat and drink to your hearts content and there won’t be anyone around to stop you! ( except maybe your bursting bellies ) Not to mention sipping on unlimited 5oz pours of all our Trippy brews, along with some special sips we’ll announce on a later date.

node.text:
🍉LIMONADA DE PATILLA🍉

How have you been beating this summer heat ? Drinking lots of water? Maybe you’re carrying a tiny fan around with you or perhaps wearing that large brimmed hat you just impulsively bought online. We decided to beat the heat by dropping another LIMONADA 🙏🏽😍👅

And what better fruit to infuse an already classically THIRST-QUENCHING beverage such as lemonade with than some PATILLA. We’re talking oceans upon oceans of mouth-watering watermelon juice, swimming with the ever so familiar lime character of this classic core beer.

Dehydration’s got nothing on us 💪🏽😤

🍉🍋🍉🍋🍉🍋🍉🍋🍉🍋

node.text:
🔥TOO TURNT TACOS🔥

Tomorrow is Friday and for us down here in SoFlo that means another wild weekend and another curated agenda of shenanigans and merriment! We all know what it takes to survive a weekend of partying in Miami and if there is one tactic that can never be forgotten is making sure you live it up with a BELLY FULL of delicious food! 🤤👅

So that’s why tomorrow, July 30th, we’re having our homies from 🌮🌮@too_turnt_taco_fl 🌮🌮come out and provide you with divine nourishment so that you may rage on into the night! Come out and snag some mad authentic chicken TINGA tacos and a 🌽 street elote 🌽so good you’ll want to stay out till the sun comes up

They’ll be slinging when we open ⏰@ 4PM⏰ So come out and grab some grub before getting TOO TURNT 

See you there  ✌🏽& ❤️

#StayTrippy #TooTurntTacos #Tacos
